/>\n冇內涵既 slogan 係得d 冇內涵既人會鍾意<br />\n4. 主角經歷左咁多野又禁忌又殺人<br />\n最後個所謂「教訓」就只係冇得用鍊金術<br />\n屌，有冇咁 on9 不過算喇大團圓結局主流觀眾鍾意<br />\n5. 其他人物刻劃都好平庸膚淺<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個世界太多垃圾漫<br />\n而且好多捧鋼鍊既人<br />\n本身都冇乜睇過漫畫<br />\n難怪會神作神作咁鳩叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa560fc58946f8307a00bf849dbda675d04f4f1","tid":964640,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c572172dee72f91dd0f1517c85fd9e2a829154","tid":964640,"uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"識等價交換=最頂端深度神作<br />\n<br />\ncyberpunk代表作,頂端作畫,儒家思想,哲學=茅人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"冇名句<br />\n<br />\n一即全 全即一   若被傷害夠<br />\n<br />\n那就是鍊金術中所說的，等價交換的原則。那時的我們深信著，這就是世界的真理。"},{"pid":"230a18f8a445e92dcf37898fc15e9d533b45ad6f","tid":964640,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c572172dee72f91dd0f1517c85fd9e2a829154","tid":964640,"uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"識等價交換=最頂端深度神作<br />\n<br />\ncyberpunk代表作,頂端作畫,儒家思想,哲學=茅人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"要講深度 / 哲學<br />\n銃夢真係高級好撚多<br />\n動作畫面又靚 100 倍<br />\n鋼鍊根本係「子供向」"},{"pid":"af1c34c36082cf8e70ecc2268509dca0123d76a6","tid":964640,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"反而刀劍就真係推動緊科技進步 真神作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多10年冇人識龍珠 但個個都識刀劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c30f04b30c4dfc574fbed6e8ea9b9aec696ae9f","tid":964640,"uid":152701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"497c6c32c462b8b960e2a1b1f64356134229b5e7","tid":964640,"uid":46849,"like":11,"dislike":32,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"鋼鍊黎講<br />\n劇情係完整<br />\n設